<h4 id="question-what-happens-when-i-create-account-">Question: What happens when i create account?</h4>
<p>Answer: When you create a new account by giving a username and password, we make a new blog and publish it on cyobb.com/username. It has all the default values and options which you can then modify by going to <a href="/update_blog">update blog details</a> page.</p>
