<h4 id="question-why-don-t-automatically-publish-changes-">Question: Why don't automatically publish changes?</h4>
<p>Answer: When creating and editing posts user's tend to create drafts. So we don't publish changes automatically and let you decide when you are ready with new stuff.</p>
